'''Callisto''' is an enormous bear empowered by the corruption of the [[Wilderness]] that resides in [[Callisto's Den]] at level 40 [[Wilderness]] and is the one of two monsters to drop the [[tyrannical ring]]. 

[[Ironman_Mode|Ironmen]] are eligible for drops from Callisto when defeating it alongside other players.

In order to enter Callisto's lair, the player must have completed the medium [[Wilderness Diary]] tasks, '''OR''' they must have a Callisto boss Slayer task (a bear Slayer task does not bypass the diary requirement). Entering the boss lair requires players to pay a fee of 50,000 coins; this fee does not need to be brought along in the inventory, and can be deducted from the bank.

